  "texts": [
    "S4 and Table S2.",
    "To further examine the molecular properties derived from simulations driven by ViSNet, we performed 500 ps MD simulations at a constant energy ensemble (NVE) for ethanol in the MD17 dataset with a time step of τ = 0.5 fs and 200 ps Ac-Ala3-NHMe in the MD22 dataset with a time step of τ = 1 fs.",
    "The simulations were driven by ViSNet, sGDML, and DFT, respectively.",
    "For ethanol, we analyzed its vibrational spectra and the probability distribution of dihedral angles.",
    "For Ac-Ala3-NHMe, we investigated its vibrational spectra and potential energy surface (PES) via the Ramachandran plot."
